template.name: OdooJobs
template.content:
Hello Advance Insight Kenya Team,

I'm Julius. SAP MM Consultant.

Your favorite online movie service.

 

I hope this email finds you well. I came across Mesozi, an Odoo implementation company based in Nairobi, and I was impressed by your reputation for providing efficient and effective ERP solutions to businesses in Kenya. As an experienced SAP implementation and support consultant, I believe my skills and expertise could be of great value to your team.

I have extensive experience in SAP implementation and have worked as a support consultant for over 3 years. During this time, I have gained valuable skills in project management, stakeholder engagement, and solution architecture. Additionally, I have experience working with various programming languages such as Python and Django, and I have a hobby project involving Odoo ERP implementation and deployment on Docker.

I am confident that my skills and experience make me a strong candidate for any opportunities that may arise within your company. Although I understand that there may not be any current job openings, I am eager to explore any possibilities for collaboration or even a future job opportunity.

I am passionate about helping businesses grow and thrive through the implementation of efficient ERP solutions, and I would love the opportunity to contribute to Mesozi's vision. Please find attached my resume for your consideration.

Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to hearing from you soon.
